🔥 Production Scenario
Problem

A developer accidentally overwrote important configuration files.

Investigation

Check repository status:

git status

Review commit history:

git log --oneline

Inspect changes:

git diff

Restore a modified file (before it's committed):

git restore README.md

Restore a deleted file from the latest commit:

git restore path/to/file
